title: CFB Week 1 preview With El Presidente, Big Cat and Rico Bosco
description:
The OG Pick Em Podcast crew is back. Pres, Big Cat and Rico break down the week 1 CFB slate, give their pre season heisman and team total win predictions, try and get to the bottom of if Pres is shooting live bullets or not much more!!!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
